_sText:
-- New content --

- 2 secret teleports to secret areas.
- bunnyhopping required to be set to 1.
- jail secret floor.
- Lasers in jail, button activation on jail secret floor
- secret floor requiring lots of speed to obtain auto sniper with 999 ammo
- jail escape from jail, shoot button on floor above with a weapon greater than your starting weapon and not a shotgun.
- jail secret floor has buyzone for each player.
- 3D skybox introduced.
- P sign to get to second floor of prison to unlock prison.
- beneath prison is secret teleport to secret floor of jail.
